'use strict'
import React from 'react'
import { Breadcrumb } from 'antd';

const {Item} = Breadcrumb
const BreadcrumbComponent = ()=>{
  return  <Breadcrumb style={{ margin: '16px 0' }}>
      <Item>Home</Item>
      <Item>List</Item>
      <Item>App</Item>
    </Breadcrumb>
}

export default BreadcrumbComponent
